Day-1
------
1. Write a raw script for Registration scenario.
2. Replace all find_element_by_xpath with generic find_element
3. Write generic functions for click, edit and select.
4. Pass locator type and locator value into tuples to generic functions.
5. Convert the value to be edited and item to be selected to keyword only arguments.

Day-2
------
6. Write a Decorator for wait and decorate all generic functions.(visible and enabled)

Day-3
------
7. Move all generic functions to class Definition. (selenium_wrapper)
8. Modify Wait decorator to handle "self".
9. Move generic functions and wait decorator into separate modules. (selenium_wrapper.py)
11. Create Login script and Registration script. And run the script individually.
12. Run Registration and login script in suite.

Day-4
------
13. Move Launching and closing browser to Conftest.py and write a fixture.
10. Create Config.py and declare all project related constants to Config class. (Config.py)
14. Parametrise the login and registration tests.

Day-5
------
15. Write POM class for Login and Registration and call methods of POM class in actual script.
16. Install pytest -html plugin and generate report. 
